title: Rural Small Business Resilience Act
ai_summary: Rural Small Business Resilience Act of 2013 passed by Congress. Act aims to help small businesses in rural areas. The bill is expected to be signed into law by the end of the year. For more information on the bill, visit http://www.cnn.com/2013/01/29/small-business-resilience-act-to-be-signed-in-october-13. Also see http://tinyurl.org/yq8qqg7.
